high_descs: Turn left then turn left again to face the counter.
Pick up the knife from the top left of the counter.
Look down at the bread.
Use the knife to slice half the bread into 8 slices.
Leave the knife on top of the bread.
Grab one slice of the bread.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the bread slice inside. Heat it for 2 seconds and take it out.
Close the microwave, turn left then turn right to face the trash can.
Put the bread slice into the trashcan.
